{"tid":244934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個可以盡快走出失戀既方法","createTime":"2017-05-15T20:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T02:04:45.000Z","uid":88967,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"921aa311082515e3c4a347f64fcbe112f67d407a","tid":244934,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:32:59.000Z","msg":"終於同男友分咗手<br />\n雖然唔係拍咗好耐，但個心都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下大家有咩方法可以快d走出失戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日喊真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我同佢之間係成日鬧交，但始終有過開心甜蜜既回憶<br />\n一諗起呢d回憶就會爆喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429a980d90edab78abdf71aa5d4d36979932c695","tid":244934,"uid":7843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:33:54.000Z","msg":"開始新感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac54530ceb3ae18b0117f09be5212f556ed0967","tid":244934,"uid":25452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:34:06.000Z","msg":"你咁唔開心點解你會用終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a7397d886fd5dcc2b66da401e823faf636827c","tid":244934,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:34:11.000Z","msg":"有冇扑過野？<br />\n冇可以搵我陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52aba2ba6ecc494413ee0d0c01ae54982754b3dc","tid":244934,"uid":88967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁唔開心點解你會用終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />