方都係咁諗？<br />\n可能得你一個咁樣覺得 人地根本唔放係眼內 無必要懷念<br />\n其實講真唔需要有回憶呢樣野 我個人從來唔諗過去<br />\n最重要係活在當下 享受現在</blockquote><br />\n但點先可以停止個腦再浮現過去二人相處既片段？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前就搵啲野黎做填滿個生活 搞到自己好忙就無時間諗野"},{"pid":"7282eaf52feed54444df522405640e660bdaca4a","tid":244934,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲開心甜蜜既回憶你肯定對方都係咁諗？<br />\n可能得你一個咁樣覺得 人地根本唔放係眼內 無必要懷念<br />\n其實講真唔需要有回憶呢樣野 我個人從來唔諗過去<br />\n最重要係活在當下 享受現在</blockquote><br />\n但點先可以停止個腦再浮現過去二人相處既片段？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前就搵啲野黎做填滿個生活 搞到自己好忙就無時間諗野</blockquote><br />\n諗翻起個陣日日都打成十幾個鐘機其實好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a645cddcfaf35ccaeb80fb37028f7dcb932ff64c","tid":244934,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:45:05.000Z","msg":"我都想知可以點？有無人可以教下我<br />\n每日都好辛苦"},{"pid":"722e2924a763c5858b7f457c0dfdfa0fa5235c57","tid":244934,"uid":73786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:47:11.000Z","msg":"諗住入來學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋日散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8bd5bece3d465a199463e8de03995019fe7c74","tid":244934,"uid":56508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T21:53:30.000Z","msg":"最辛苦係佢同我分手之後又搵返我"},{"pid":"b83555ccd865724d38391f29c3280772a497a27b","tid":244934,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最辛苦係佢同我分手之後又搵返我</blockquote><br />\n鎖晒佢所有聯絡方式啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  留係到有咩用"},{"pid":"6b455d2f1c3a18f320ba7a10f1338d178ea8c93